name: Friday Night Funkin' - A World of Our Own
name_original: Friday Night Funkin' - A World of Our Own
description:
Somehow, BF and GF have ended up in Paw-Tucket, the world created by pets, for pets, where there's (usually) no humans around.
What better to do than have rap battles with some of Paw-Tucket's best singers? Be careful though, some of the denizens aren't quite as keen on letting a human enter Paw-Tucket without punishment...
